Since we just care about the commit stats, not the commit content, so
when meet the decode error, just ignore, as it must happened in the
commit content. If not have a better solution.

Fix the 'utf-8' codec can't decode( simplejson ) bug.

If the data fetched include gbk edcoded content(e.g. Chinese), it'll met
this bug.

Fix the Null Author bug.

When the commit author or commuter is not stetted, fetch data will
result error. Met this bug from frankyue's commits of Aug. 8th.
